I have a PPK in excellent condition. Like to trade to a Sig but open to other offers

I've gotten several questions about the German markings on the slide: 

The gun is a .380 but is marked 9mm kurz on the slide because kurz is German for "short." 9mm kurz, or short, and .380 rounds are the same thing, just different names. So basically it is for the German and American reference. Which also explains why in Bond movies they refer to his guns as 9mm, when in reality Bond is carrying the .380 PPK as offered here.
